title: Indecent Demise - Born To The Dead EP 320kbps (Melodic Death Met
description:
Indecent Demise's second, and last EP.


Indecent Demise is a young band from Pittsburgh, PA influenced from acts such as The Black Dahlia Murder, Whitechapel, As Blood Runs Black and much more. After 2 very interesting years of being together we have decided to move on to bigger and better things in our lives. Long live the metal community, may the Internet be her lifeboat! Or her demise...

Thanks for listening!!
